calculation.original_formula:
IF SUM([Sales]) > 70000 THEN "High"
ELSEIF SUM([Sales]) >= 35000 AND SUM([Sales]) < 70000 THEN "Medium"
ELSEIF SUM([Sales]) < 35000 THEN "Low"
END
